# Student Profiles Starter

This project implements the very basics of the `StudentProfiles` project.

## Quickstart

```bash
; dotnet test # To run tests
```

## Starting Data Model

* One student can have zero or more notes.

```
┌───────────────┐
│               │
│    Student    │
│               │
└───────┬───────┘
        │
        │
        │
┌──────/|\──────┐
│               │
│     Note      │
│               │
└───────────────┘
```
